# Background Image Placeholder

This file serves as a placeholder for the optional background image system.

To use a background image instead of the gradient:
1. Replace this file with your desired background image (background.jpg)
2. Uncomment the background image line in assets/css/responsive.css
3. The image will be applied as a full-screen background

Recommended specifications:
- Format: JPG or WebP
- Resolution: 1920x1080 or higher
- File size: Under 500KB for optimal performance
- Content: Subtle pattern or texture that doesn't interfere with text readability